<2ND_LINE>BC-Gangs-Fearless Neighbors, Adv 29, 1st Ld-Writethru, b0752,0898</2ND_LINE>
<NOTE>$Adv29</NOTE>
<NOTE>For Release Sunday, May 29, and Thereafter</NOTE>
<NOTE>Eds: SUBS 5th graf, ``I get...,'' to CORRECT colors to black and
